WEBVTT

00:00:17.199 --> 00:00:21.879
In the 15th year of the reign of Tiberius Caesar,

00:00:21.879 --> 00:00:25.960
when Pontius Pilate was governor of Judea,

00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:29.879
Herod was district ruler of Galilee.

00:00:29.879 --> 00:00:31.879
Philip, his brother, was district ruler

00:00:31.879 --> 00:00:36.469
of the country of Iteria and Trachonitis,

00:00:36.469 --> 00:00:44.299
and Lysanius was district ruler of Abelene

00:00:44.299 --> 00:00:50.460
in the days of chief priest Annus and of Caeophus.

00:00:50.460 --> 00:00:55.619
God's declaration came to John,

00:00:55.859 --> 00:01:03.280
the son of Zechariah, the wilderness.

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:08.040
This man came as a witness

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:15.310
in order to bear witness about the light

00:01:15.310 --> 00:01:17.790
so that people of all sorts

00:01:17.790 --> 00:01:23.140
might believe through him.

00:01:23.140 --> 00:01:26.670
He was not that light,

00:01:26.670 --> 00:02:36.139
but he was meant to bear witness about that light.

00:02:36.139 --> 00:02:40.340
In those days,

00:02:40.340 --> 00:02:43.020
John the Baptist came preaching

00:02:43.020 --> 00:02:46.949
in the wilderness of Judea.

00:02:46.949 --> 00:02:55.439
Repent for the kingdom of the heavens has drawn near.

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:13.520
So he went into all the country around the Jordan,

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:18.719
preaching baptism in symbol of repentance

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:26.419
for forgiveness of sins.

00:03:26.419 --> 00:03:28.099
Just as it is written in the book

00:03:28.099 --> 00:03:32.289
of the words of Isaiah the prophet,

00:03:32.289 --> 00:03:35.409
a voice of one crying out in the wilderness,

00:03:36.409 --> 00:03:38.810
prepare the way of Jehovah,

00:03:40.409 --> 00:03:45.509
make his roads straight,

00:03:45.509 --> 00:03:49.580
every valley must be filled up,

00:03:49.580 --> 00:03:54.860
and every mountain and hill leveled.

00:03:54.860 --> 00:04:00.219
The crooked ways must become straight

00:04:00.219 --> 00:04:14.930
and the rough ways smooth,

00:04:14.930 --> 00:04:16.970
and all flesh will see

00:04:18.209 --> 00:04:33.129
the salvation of God.

00:04:33.129 --> 00:04:36.569
Now John was clothed with camel's air

00:04:36.649 --> 00:04:39.730
and had a leather belt around his waist.

00:04:39.730 --> 00:04:56.750
His food was locusts and wild honey

00:04:56.750 --> 00:05:00.670
then the people of Jerusalem and all Judea

00:05:00.670 --> 00:05:03.230
and all the country around the Jordan

00:05:03.230 --> 00:05:12.300
were going out to him

00:05:12.300 --> 00:05:15.620
and they were baptized by him in the Jordan River.

00:05:15.620 --> 00:05:37.730
Openly confessing their sins

00:05:37.730 --> 00:05:40.529
when he caught sight of many of the Pharisees

00:05:40.529 --> 00:05:47.740
and Sadducees coming to the baptism.

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:48.740
He said to them,

00:05:49.740 --> 00:05:51.740
You offspring of vipers

00:05:51.740 --> 00:05:57.399
who has warned you to flee from the coming wrath.

00:05:59.399 --> 00:06:10.819
Therefore, produce fruit that befits repentance,

00:06:10.819 --> 00:06:13.819
do not presume to say to yourselves,

00:06:13.819 --> 00:06:15.819
we have Abraham as our Father.

00:06:15.819 --> 00:06:20.259
For I say to you,

00:06:20.259 --> 00:06:24.259
that God is able to raise up children for Abraham

00:06:24.259 --> 00:06:26.259
from these stones.

00:06:28.629 --> 00:06:34.939
The axe is already lying at the root of the trees,

00:06:34.939 --> 00:06:38.699
every tree then that does not produce fine fruit.

00:06:40.300 --> 00:07:20.160
It's to be cut down and thrown into the fire

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:21.839
and the crowns were asking him,

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:24.879
what then should we do?

00:07:26.639 --> 00:07:30.879
Let the man who has two garments share with the man who has none

00:07:31.879 --> 00:07:34.240
and let the one who has something to eat do the same.

00:07:35.240 --> 00:07:38.240
Even tax collectors came to be baptized.

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:40.240
Teacher!

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:42.240
What should we do?

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:56.379
Do not demand anything more than the tax rate.

00:07:56.379 --> 00:08:02.420
Also, those in military service were asking him,

00:08:02.420 --> 00:08:07.740
what should we do to not harass anybody

00:08:07.740 --> 00:08:09.740
or accuse anybody falsely

00:08:09.740 --> 00:08:14.269
but be satisfied with your provisions?

00:08:14.269 --> 00:08:19.000
Now the people were in expectation

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:24.000
and all of them were reasoning in their hearts about John.

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:28.730
May he perhaps be the Christ?

00:08:28.730 --> 00:08:32.730
John gave the answer, saying to all,

00:08:32.730 --> 00:08:34.730
I, for my part,

00:08:34.730 --> 00:08:38.899
baptized you with the water

00:08:38.899 --> 00:08:40.899
that the one stronger than I am is coming,

00:08:40.899 --> 00:08:44.899
the less of whose sandals I am not worthy to one die.

00:08:44.899 --> 00:08:47.899
He will baptize you with holy spirit

00:08:47.899 --> 00:08:49.899
and with fire,

00:08:49.899 --> 00:08:51.899
his winnowing shovel is in his hand

00:08:51.899 --> 00:08:55.899
to clean up his dressing floor completely,

00:08:55.899 --> 00:08:59.899
and together the wheat into his stoy else.

00:08:59.899 --> 00:09:05.580
But the chaff,

00:09:05.580 --> 00:09:38.600
he will burn up with fire that cannot be put out.

00:09:38.600 --> 00:09:41.600
He also gave many other exhortations

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:47.009
and continued declaring good news to the people.

00:09:47.009 --> 00:11:50.590
Then Jesus came from Galilee

00:11:50.590 --> 00:11:56.759
to the Jordan to John

00:11:56.759 --> 00:11:58.759
in order to be baptized by him.

00:11:58.759 --> 00:12:06.120
But the latter tried to prevent him.

00:12:06.120 --> 00:12:11.610
I'm the one who needs to be baptized by you.

00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:15.019
Are you coming to me?

00:12:15.019 --> 00:12:21.370
Let it be this time.

00:12:21.370 --> 00:12:24.370
For in that way, it is suitable for us

00:12:24.370 --> 00:12:26.370
to carry out all that is righteous.

00:12:26.370 --> 00:12:35.340
Then he quit preventing him,

00:12:35.340 --> 00:13:22.440
after being baptized.

00:13:22.440 --> 00:13:25.440
Jesus immediately came up from the water.

00:13:25.440 --> 00:14:07.730
Heavens were opened up

00:14:07.730 --> 00:14:13.490
and he saw God's spirit descending

00:14:13.490 --> 00:14:16.490
