00:14:16.490 --> 00:14:24.440
and coming upon him.

00:14:24.440 --> 00:14:29.440
Also, a voice from the heavens said,

00:14:29.440 --> 00:14:32.440
This is my son,

00:14:32.440 --> 00:14:35.440
the beloved whom I have...

00:14:35.440 --> 00:15:21.990
And immediately,

00:15:21.990 --> 00:15:23.990
the spirit impelled him

00:15:23.990 --> 00:15:25.990
to go into the wilderness

00:15:25.990 --> 00:15:37.429
so he continued in the wilderness for forty days,

00:15:37.429 --> 00:15:40.429
being tempted by Satan.

00:15:40.429 --> 00:15:43.429
He was with the wild beasts.

00:15:43.429 --> 00:15:53.840
But the angels were ministering to him.

00:15:53.840 --> 00:15:57.220
