00:21:46.289 --> 00:21:55.240
If you are son of God,

00:21:55.240 --> 00:22:01.950
tell these stones,

00:22:01.950 --> 00:22:03.950
to become loaves of bread,

00:22:03.950 --> 00:22:12.539
it is written,

00:22:12.539 --> 00:22:14.539
man must live not on bread alone,

00:22:14.539 --> 00:22:21.440
but on every word that comes

00:22:21.440 --> 00:22:43.500
from Jehovah's mouth.

00:22:43.500 --> 00:22:44.500
Then the devil took him along

00:22:44.500 --> 00:22:46.500
into the holy city,

00:22:46.500 --> 00:22:47.500
and he stationed him

00:22:47.500 --> 00:22:49.500
on the battlement of the temple,

00:22:49.500 --> 00:22:52.500
and said to him,

00:22:52.500 --> 00:22:56.500
If you are a son of God,

00:22:56.500 --> 00:23:01.359
throw yourself down,

00:23:01.359 --> 00:23:04.359
for it is written,

00:23:04.359 --> 00:23:06.359
he will give his angels

00:23:06.359 --> 00:23:09.359
a command concerning you,

00:23:09.359 --> 00:23:12.359
and they will carry you on their hands,

00:23:12.359 --> 00:23:15.359
so that you may not strike your foot

00:23:15.359 --> 00:23:17.359
against the stones.

00:23:17.359 --> 00:23:20.359
Again, it is written,

00:23:20.359 --> 00:23:22.359
you must not put Jehovah

00:23:22.359 --> 00:23:42.119
your God to the test.

00:23:42.119 --> 00:23:46.009
So he brought him up,

00:23:46.009 --> 00:23:48.009
and showed him all the kingdoms

00:23:48.009 --> 00:23:50.009
of the inhabited earth,

00:23:50.009 --> 00:24:09.549
in an instant of time.

00:24:09.549 --> 00:24:12.549
Then the devil said to him,

00:24:12.549 --> 00:24:16.549
I will give you all this authority,

00:24:16.549 --> 00:24:21.059
and their glory,

00:24:21.059 --> 00:24:26.559
because it has been handed over to me,

00:24:26.559 --> 00:24:30.559
and I give it to whoever I wish,

00:24:30.559 --> 00:24:38.099
if you therefore,

00:24:38.099 --> 00:24:41.099
do an act of worship,

00:24:41.099 --> 00:24:43.099
before me,

00:24:43.099 --> 00:24:46.740
it will all be yours.

00:24:46.740 --> 00:24:48.740
Go away, Satan,

00:24:48.740 --> 00:24:50.740
for it is written,

00:24:50.740 --> 00:24:52.740
it is Jehovah your God,

00:24:52.740 --> 00:24:53.740
you must worship,

00:24:53.740 --> 00:24:55.740
and it is to him alone,

00:24:55.740 --> 00:25:02.380
you must render sacred service.

00:25:02.380 --> 00:25:04.380
Then,

00:25:04.380 --> 00:25:31.619
the devil left him.

00:25:31.619 --> 00:25:32.619
Angels came,

00:25:43.119 --> 00:25:45.119
and began to minister to him.

00:25:45.119 --> 00:27:30.059
This is the witness John gave,

00:27:30.059 --> 00:27:32.059
when the Jews sent priests

00:27:32.059 --> 00:27:34.059
and Levites from Jerusalem

00:27:34.059 --> 00:27:40.599
to ask him,

00:27:40.599 --> 00:27:42.599
Who are you?

00:27:42.599 --> 00:27:44.599
And he admitted it,

00:27:44.599 --> 00:27:46.599
and did not deny it.

00:27:46.599 --> 00:27:48.599
I am not the Christ.

00:27:48.599 --> 00:27:50.599
What then?

00:27:50.599 --> 00:27:52.599
Are you Elijah?

00:27:52.599 --> 00:27:56.579
I am not.

00:27:56.579 --> 00:27:58.579
Are you the prophet?

00:27:58.579 --> 00:28:00.579
No.

00:28:00.579 --> 00:28:03.579
Who are you?

00:28:03.579 --> 00:28:04.579
Tell us,

00:28:04.579 --> 00:28:07.579
so that we may give an answer to those who sent us.

00:28:07.579 --> 00:28:19.700
What do you say about yourself?

00:28:19.700 --> 00:28:23.339
I am a voice,

00:28:24.339 --> 00:28:27.339
of someone crying out in the wilderness,

00:28:27.339 --> 00:28:30.339
make the way of Jehovah's straight,

00:28:30.339 --> 00:28:33.339
just as Isaiah the prophet said.

00:28:33.339 --> 00:28:37.339
Now those sent were from the Pharisees,

00:28:37.339 --> 00:28:40.339
so they questioned him.

00:28:40.339 --> 00:28:42.339
Why then do you baptize,

00:28:42.339 --> 00:28:46.339
if you are not the Christ or Elijah or the prophet?

00:28:46.339 --> 00:28:49.339
I baptize in water,

00:28:49.339 --> 00:28:51.339
understanding among you,

00:28:51.339 --> 00:28:53.339
not know,

00:28:53.339 --> 00:28:55.339
the one coming behind me,

00:28:55.339 --> 00:29:01.019
the lace of whose sandal,

00:29:01.019 --> 00:29:03.019
I am not worthy to untie.

00:29:03.019 --> 00:29:27.690
These things took place in Bethany across the Jordan,

00:29:27.690 --> 00:29:32.920
where John was baptizing.

00:29:32.920 --> 00:29:54.940
The next day, he saw Jesus coming toward him.

00:29:54.940 --> 00:30:07.829
See, the Lamb of God,

00:30:07.829 --> 00:30:13.200
who takes away the sin of the world.

00:30:13.200 --> 00:30:15.200
This is the one,

00:30:15.200 --> 00:30:17.200
about whom I said behind me,

00:30:17.200 --> 00:30:20.200
as a man was advanced in front of me,

00:30:20.200 --> 00:30:22.200
for he existed before me.

00:30:22.200 --> 00:30:25.200
Even I did not know him,

00:30:25.200 --> 00:30:28.200
but the reason why I came baptizing in water

00:30:28.200 --> 00:30:32.509
was so that he might be made manifest to Israel.

00:30:32.509 --> 00:30:35.509
I viewed the Spirit coming down as a dove,

00:30:35.509 --> 00:30:37.509
out of heaven,

00:30:37.509 --> 00:30:40.509
and it remained upon him.

00:30:40.509 --> 00:30:42.509
Even I did not know him,

00:30:42.509 --> 00:30:45.509
but the very one who sent me to baptizing water said to me,

00:30:45.509 --> 00:30:49.509
whoever it is upon whom you see the Spirit coming down and remaining.

00:30:49.509 --> 00:30:51.509
This is the one,

00:30:51.509 --> 00:30:54.509
who baptizes in Holy Spirit.

00:30:54.509 --> 00:30:57.509
And I have seen it,

00:30:57.509 --> 00:30:59.509
and I've given witness,

00:30:59.509 --> 00:31:21.460
that this one is the Son of God.

00:31:21.460 --> 00:31:25.380
Again, the next day,

00:31:25.380 --> 00:31:32.089
John was standing with two of his disciples,

00:31:32.089 --> 00:31:34.089
and as he looked at Jesus walking,

00:31:34.089 --> 00:31:36.089
