00:32:14.730 --> 00:32:17.730
What are you looking for?

00:32:17.730 --> 00:32:25.400
Rabbi, where are you staying?

00:32:25.400 --> 00:32:27.400
Come, and you'll see.

00:32:27.400 --> 00:32:32.940
So they went,

00:32:32.940 --> 00:32:34.940
and saw where he was staying,

00:32:34.940 --> 00:32:37.940
and they stayed with him that day.

00:32:37.940 --> 00:32:39.940
It was about the tenth hour.

00:32:39.940 --> 00:32:44.740
Andrew, the brother of Simon Peter,

00:32:44.740 --> 00:32:47.740
was one of the two who heard what John said,

00:32:47.740 --> 00:32:54.309
and followed Jesus.

00:32:54.309 --> 00:32:59.329
He first found his own brother, Simon.

00:32:59.329 --> 00:33:11.259
We have found the Messiah,

00:33:11.259 --> 00:33:19.660
and he led him to Jesus.

00:33:19.660 --> 00:33:33.539
And you, Simon,

00:33:33.539 --> 00:33:34.539
the Son of John,

00:33:34.539 --> 00:33:41.369
will be called Seifas.

00:33:41.369 --> 00:33:55.740
The next day,

00:33:55.740 --> 00:33:57.740
he wanted to leave for Galilee.

00:33:57.740 --> 00:34:10.179
Jesus then found,

00:34:10.179 --> 00:34:11.179
Philip,

00:34:11.179 --> 00:34:14.480
and said to him,

00:34:14.480 --> 00:34:17.889
Be my follower.

00:34:17.889 --> 00:34:21.550
Now Philip was from Bethseder,

00:34:21.550 --> 00:34:24.550
from the city of Andrew and Peter.

00:34:24.550 --> 00:34:30.389
Philip found,

00:34:30.389 --> 00:34:32.389
Nathaniel.

00:34:32.389 --> 00:34:39.579
Nathaniel.

00:34:39.579 --> 00:34:40.579
We have found the one,

00:34:40.579 --> 00:34:42.579
of whom Moses,

00:34:42.579 --> 00:34:44.579
in the law and the prophets wrote,

00:34:44.579 --> 00:34:45.579
Jesus,

00:34:45.579 --> 00:34:47.579
the Son of Joseph,

00:34:47.579 --> 00:34:49.579
from Nazareth.

00:34:49.579 --> 00:34:55.739
Can anything good come out of Nazareth?

00:34:55.739 --> 00:35:22.760
Come and see.

00:35:22.760 --> 00:35:24.760
Jesus saw Nathaniel coming toward him,

00:35:24.760 --> 00:35:26.760
and said about him.

00:35:26.760 --> 00:35:28.760
See,

00:35:28.760 --> 00:35:30.760
truly,

00:35:30.760 --> 00:35:31.760
an Israelite,

00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:34.760
in whom there is no deceit.

00:35:34.760 --> 00:35:35.760
How do you know me?

00:35:35.760 --> 00:35:45.980
Before Philip called you,

00:35:45.980 --> 00:35:47.980
while you're under the fig tree.

00:35:47.980 --> 00:35:49.980
I saw you.

00:35:49.980 --> 00:36:04.460
Rabbi,

00:36:04.460 --> 00:36:07.460
you are the Son of God.

00:36:07.460 --> 00:36:11.460
You are King of Israel.

00:36:11.460 --> 00:36:12.460
Do you believe,

00:36:12.460 --> 00:36:15.460
because I told you I saw you're under the fig tree?

00:36:15.460 --> 00:36:18.460
You will see things greater than these.

00:36:18.460 --> 00:36:21.460
It was truly I say to you, man.

00:36:21.460 --> 00:36:24.460
You will see heaven opened up,

00:36:24.460 --> 00:36:25.460
and the angels of God

00:36:25.460 --> 00:36:27.460
are sending and descending,

00:36:27.460 --> 00:36:28.460
to the Son of Man.

00:36:28.460 --> 00:37:03.800
And on the third day,

00:37:03.800 --> 00:37:06.800
a marriage feast took place,

00:37:06.800 --> 00:37:21.059
in Cana of Galilee,

00:37:21.059 --> 00:37:27.860
and the mother of Jesus was there.

00:37:27.860 --> 00:37:29.860
Jesus and his disciples

00:37:29.860 --> 00:37:31.860
were also invited to the marriage feast,

00:37:31.860 --> 00:38:25.340
on the wine-red short.

00:38:25.340 --> 00:38:28.340
The mother of Jesus said to him,

00:38:28.340 --> 00:38:37.059
they have no wine.

00:38:37.059 --> 00:38:45.019
Why has that of concern to me to you?

00:38:45.019 --> 00:39:21.679
My hour has not yet come.

00:39:21.679 --> 00:39:25.019
His mother said to those serving.

00:39:25.019 --> 00:39:32.210
Do whatever he tells you.

00:39:32.210 --> 00:39:35.210
Now there were six stone water jars sitting there,

00:39:35.210 --> 00:39:39.210
as required by the purification rules of the Jews.

00:39:39.210 --> 00:39:42.210
Each able to hold two or three liquid measures.

00:39:42.210 --> 00:39:49.739
Fill the jars with water.

00:39:49.739 --> 00:41:15.170
So they filled them

00:41:15.170 --> 00:41:16.170
to the brim.

00:41:16.170 --> 00:41:55.610
Draw some out,

00:41:55.610 --> 00:42:17.480
and take it to the director of the feast.

00:42:17.480 --> 00:42:19.480
So they took it.

00:42:19.480 --> 00:42:39.780
When the director of the feast

00:42:39.780 --> 00:42:43.780
tasted the water that had now been turned into wine,

00:42:43.780 --> 00:42:45.780
not knowing where it came from,

00:42:45.780 --> 00:42:48.780
although the servants who had drawn out the water knew.

00:42:48.780 --> 00:42:59.940
The director of the feast called the bridegroom

00:42:59.940 --> 00:43:00.940
and said to him,

00:43:00.940 --> 00:43:06.349
everyone else looked out the fine wine first.

00:43:06.349 --> 00:43:09.349
And when people are intoxicated,

00:43:09.349 --> 00:43:31.219
the inferior you have saved the fine wine until now.

00:43:31.219 --> 00:43:34.219
Jesus did this encana of Galilee

00:43:34.219 --> 00:43:36.219
as the beginning of his signs,

00:43:36.219 --> 00:43:50.070
and he made his glory manifest,

00:43:50.070 --> 00:43:53.070
and his disciples put their faith in him.

00:43:53.070 --> 00:44:12.480
After this,

00:44:12.480 --> 00:44:14.480
he and his mother,

00:44:14.480 --> 00:44:17.480
and his brothers and his disciples,

00:44:17.480 --> 00:44:19.480
went down to Capernaum,

00:44:19.480 --> 00:44:26.960
but they did not stay there many days.

00:44:26.960 --> 00:45:36.780
Now the Passover of the Jews was near,

00:45:36.780 --> 00:45:38.780
and Jesus went up to Jerusalem.

00:45:38.780 --> 00:46:31.280
He found in the temple,

00:46:31.280 --> 00:46:33.280
those selling cattle,

00:46:33.280 --> 00:46:35.280
and sheep,

00:46:35.280 --> 00:46:37.280
and doves.

00:46:37.280 --> 00:46:42.989
For a sheep of this quality,

00:46:42.989 --> 00:46:43.989
why do you ask for more?

00:46:43.989 --> 00:46:45.989
That is the price.

00:46:45.989 --> 00:46:47.989
This is all we have.

00:46:47.989 --> 00:47:10.250
Money brokers in their seats.

00:47:10.250 --> 00:48:39.420
After making a whip of ropes,

00:48:39.420 --> 00:48:48.239
he drove all those with the sheep and cattle

00:48:48.239 --> 00:48:49.239
out of the temple,

00:48:49.239 --> 00:48:59.789
and he poured out the coins of the money changes,

00:48:59.789 --> 00:49:21.250
turned their tables,

00:49:21.250 --> 00:49:23.250
and he said to those selling the doves.

00:49:23.250 --> 00:49:26.849
Take these things away from here.

00:49:26.849 --> 00:49:47.059
Stop making a house of my father.

00:49:47.059 --> 00:49:49.059
A house of commerce.

00:49:49.059 --> 00:49:56.159
His disciples recalled that it is written,

00:49:56.159 --> 00:50:01.570
the zeal for your house will consume me.

00:50:01.570 --> 00:50:11.469
What sign can you show us

00:50:11.469 --> 00:50:16.519
since you're doing these things?

00:50:16.519 --> 00:50:19.519
Tehran, this temple,

00:50:19.519 --> 00:50:23.519
in three days, I will raise it up.

00:50:23.519 --> 00:50:28.519
This temple was built in 46 years.

00:50:28.519 --> 00:50:32.519
And will you raise it up in three days?

00:50:32.519 --> 00:50:35.519
But he was talking about the temple of his body.

00:50:35.519 --> 00:50:40.960
When, though, he was raised up from the dead,

00:50:40.960 --> 00:50:44.960
his disciples recalled that he used to say this,

00:50:44.960 --> 00:50:47.960
and they believed in this scripture,

00:50:47.960 --> 00:50:49.960
and what Jesus had spoken,

00:50:49.960 --> 00:51:20.739
when he was in Jerusalem at the festival of the Passover.

00:51:20.739 --> 00:51:23.739
Many people put their faith in his name,

00:51:23.739 --> 00:51:25.739
when they saw the signs that he was performing,

00:51:25.739 --> 00:51:58.730
but Jesus would not entrust himself to them,

00:51:58.730 --> 00:52:02.360
because he knew them all,

00:52:02.360 --> 00:52:27.260
and because he did not need to have anyone there witness about man.

00:52:27.260 --> 00:52:32.079
For he knew what was in man.
